Daniel,

I love your idea.  However I was kind of hoping for an event based
system.  What I would like to do is to tie together ddccontrol and
synergy.  I would love to use the source button on my monitor to trigger
synergy to change systems.  This would completely eliminate my need for
a KVM switch.  Especially since I have this wonderful monitor with a vga
and dmi input and a source button on it :)

Autorotation would also be sweet.

I have a KVM switch but its incompatible with my new motherboard.  The
mouse simply does not work.

Thanks,
David



